#Selectors

Conecta um elemento HTML com o CSS 

##Tipos

* Global selector '*'
* Element/Type selector 'h1, h2, p, div'
* ID Selector '#box, #container '
* Class Selector '.red, .m-4 '
* Atribute Selector, pseudo-class, pseudo-element, e outros 

